  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t从一尊到各层五毛小粉红，都把没有对外殖民和掠夺当成巨大光荣。所谓“我们一不输出革命，二不输出贫困饥饿……”，“中国不对外侵略……”<br/>\n<br/>\r\n那TMD你们殖民和掠夺同胞，是不是比其他殖民国家更为可耻？<br/>\n<br/>\r\n还嘲笑同胞中的弱势群体悲惨。这不就是恨国党制造机吗？<br/>\n<br/>\r\n而那些被剥削奴役还当中共拥护者的中下层国人，则更贱。纳粹德国和天皇日本，毕竟侵略外国，国民支持有利可图。中共则是像满清一样，把国人当奴隶使用。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n不过现在越来越多人明白了清醒了<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNTJkMzhmOGIzZjAxOWFhNDBkMDUzLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/52d38f8b3f019aa40d053.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/52d38f8b3f019aa40d053.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/52d38f8b3f019aa40d053.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvNzI0Y2E5MTRmYzg3ZDc1ZmU4MTZmLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/724ca914fc87d75fe816f.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/724ca914fc87d75fe816f.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/724ca914fc87d75fe816f.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMjBhOTgwM2NkYzQ1ZDI1NzA4ZGUyLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/20a9803cdc45d25708de2.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/20a9803cdc45d25708de2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/20a9803cdc45d25708de2.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMThhODMzNDBiNjFmNGQ1ZThkNTI2LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/18a83340b61f4d5e8d526.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/18a83340b61f4d5e8d526.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/18a83340b61f4d5e8d526.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
